UR":null,"euaVerified":null,"euaEstimated":null,"euaPurchased":null,"euaBalance":null}}]},"remarkList":[{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-12T12:31:55.503","modifiedByFull":"Rasmussen, Nadia","remark":"Port cost updated, Corpus Christi USD -18.602,46 (already incl. as charterers costs)"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-07T14:58:53.07","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"Charterers expense was rebilled accordingly increasing TCE up 2k/day"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-03-04T20:22:29.493","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"After long ballast from Argentina vessel took bunkers at Bolivar Roads prior loading in Corpus, unfortunately the weather did not cooperate leading to 48H bunker only call. Vessel berthed on arrival at Corpus but as she was approaching berth lost forward and aft propulsion leading to a 14H delay for repairs. Luckily Valero terminal allowed vessel to remain alongside overnight and by the next morning all was completed and vessel commenced loading. Balance voyage went off without major issue, there were some grumblings from charterers about vessel not discharging grades simultaneously but they ultimately refused to sign LOI for shared vapor return line so we continued. Vessel spent 7 days in St. Croix for discharge/reload, and called 2 berths in Nassau. $53k dockage at Corpus has been rebilled along with $78k in costs associated with the second berth in Bahamas. Speed up to St. Croix also billed at $10.5k and final demurrage claim sent for 8 days @ 34kpdpr. She\u0027s now loading at St. Rose for Marquis COA."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-12T15:19:21.807","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"days extended at Limetree Bay, demurrage est increased 2 days"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-06T13:10:30.497","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"discharge/reload time extended at Limetree Bay - 2 days added to demurrage estimate"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-02T21:22:20.233","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"vessel lost propulsion while docking in CC. 14h to repair"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-23T17:08:19.133","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"added 135k option to call bahamas after antigua  //  added  75k option to call antigua after st. croix"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-23T17:00:09.13","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"48H @Bolivar Roads for bunkers - high winds and thunderstorms delayed bunkers delivery by ~36H"}],"offhireList":[{"id":197423,"dateStartUtc":"2024-01-24T18:30:00","dateEndUtc":"2024-01-25T09:42:00","days":0.6333333333333333,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":"Engine","remark":"unplanned propulsion failure","offhireBunkerList":[{"id":254797,"gradeName":"LSGO","quantity":2.0,"price":890.0,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}